d vector art. With features like ''Regenerate'' and import functionality, users can easily overcome creative blocks and remix designs. The tool promotes collaboration within a community of designers and seamlessly integrates into existing design workflows.', NULL, '["AI Tools","Community Collaboration","Workflow Integration"]');
INSERT INTO products (id,created_at,name,url,website_image_url,icon_url,meta,description,category_id,subcategory) VALUES ('ed14238f-c677-486b-8fec-2c9488adb8a0', '2024-04-12T15:28:12.569Z', 'Chat2Stats', 'https://2stats.chat/', 'images/chat2stats.webp', 'images/chat2stats-icon.webp', '{"what":"Chat2Stats is a data analysis tool powered with chatGPT. It allows users to input their data and have natural language conversations to gain insights without the need for SQL queries. The tool also offers a self-hosted version for more control over data privacy and security.","who":"Chat2Stats is designed for data analysts, business professionals, researchers, and anyone looking to easily analyze and gain insights from their data through natural language interactions. It is suitable for individuals and teams across various industries.","best_features":["Natural language interaction for data analysis, making it user-friendly and accessible to non-technical users.","Self-hosted version available for enhanced data security and privacy compliance.","Insightful data analysis without the need for complex SQL queries, streamlining the analysis process."]}', 'Chat2Stats is a data analysis tool that leverages chatGPT technology to provide users with a seamless and intuitive way to analyze data. By enabling natural language interactions, users can easily explore and gain insights from their data without the need for technical expertise or SQL queries. The self-hosted version offers additional control over data security and privacy, making it a versatile tool for individuals and teams in various industries.', NULL, '["AI Tools","Data Analysis","Chat Solutions"]');
INSERT INTO products (id,created_at,name,url,website_image_url,icon_url,meta,description,category_id,subcategory) VALUES ('9dbc43f7-25ed-4258-8aab-569225a6a53f', '2024-04-12T15:28:12.570Z', 'Chat360', 'https://chat360.io/', 'images/chat360.webp', 'images/chat360-icon.webp', '{"what":"Chat360 is a conversational AI chatbot builder designed to enhance customer engagement and conversion through omnichannel platforms and various integrations.","who":"Chat360 is for businesses of all sizes and industries looking to scale through conversational sales, marketing, and customer support.","best_features":["Compatibility with popular platforms like WhatsApp, Facebook Messenger, Instagram, and websites","Various integrations with Google Sheets, Shopify, Stripe, Gmail, and more","No-code interface for easy bot creation and lead generation"],"pricing":[]}', 'Chat360 is a comprehensive conversational AI chatbot builder that enables businesses to reach customers through their preferred channels, automate Instagram DMs and Facebook Messenger, and prioritize lead generation. It offers features for WhatsApp Business API, lead generation, customer support, and conversational marketing. Trusted by global brand leaders, Chat360''s resource center provides access to blogs, guides, and partnership options.', NULL, '["AI Agents","Customer Communication","Marketing"]');
