nsights without the tedium of traditional forms. Users can create interview guides, share interview links, and review transcripts and insights gathered by AI agents. The platform offers ready-to-use templates for various interview purposes and caters to a wide range of users, including HR teams, hiring managers, recruiters, product managers, developers, UX designers, market researchers, content creators, journalists, and marketing teams.', NULL, '["Interview Automation","Insight Generation","Template-based Interviews"]');
